      "subject": "Welcome to the OLYMPUS Builder Dashboard",
      "preview": "You're one step closer to full visibility and control over your builds",
      "body": "Hey there,\n\nWelcome to the OLYMPUS Builder Dashboard! I'm excited to show you how this tool can transform the way you approach software development.\n\nOver the next few days, I'll be sending you a series of emails that dive deeper into the key features and benefits of the dashboard. But first, let me give you a quick overview...\n\nThe OLYMPUS Builder Dashboard is designed to give you complete transparency into your build process - from start to finish. No more wondering what's really happening or trying to piece together information from multiple sources.\n\nInstead, you'll have a centralized hub that shows you the real-time status of your builds, the timeline of key phases, the agents involved, and the critical decisions being made. It's like having an expert project manager and QA team built right into your workflow.\n\nBy the end of this welcome sequence, you'll know exactly how to leverage the OLYMPUS Dashboard to ship your software with confidence. Keep an eye on your inbox for the next email coming soon.\n\nTo your building success,\n[Your Name]\nOLYMPUS Conversion Copywriter",
