{
  "page_blueprint": {
    "page_type": "sales_page",
    "sections": [
      {
        "id": "hero",
        "order": 1,
        "type": "hero",
        "headline": "Unlock the Power of Your Builds with Olympus Builder Dashboard",
        "subheadline": "Gain unprecedented visibility and control over your complex software projects.",
        "cta": {
          "text": "Get Started Now",
          "style": "primary",
          "urgency": true
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "problem",
        "order": 2,
        "type": "problem",
        "body": "Building software is hard. Keeping track of all the moving parts, coordinating your team, and ensuring your project stays on track can feel like an uphill battle. You've tried project management tools, Gantt charts, and status meetings, but they just add more complexity without giving you the clarity you need."
      },
      {
        "id": "agitation",
        "order": 3,
        "type": "agitation",
        "body": "If nothing changes, your builds will continue to be plagued by delays, cost overruns, and the nagging feeling that you're missing something critical. Your team will get frustrated, your stakeholders will lose confidence, and your reputation will suffer. The stress of running software projects will only intensify, leaving you feeling powerless to regain control."
      },
      {
        "id": "solution",
        "order": 4,
        "type": "solution",
        "body": "There's a better way. Introducing the Olympus Builder Dashboard - the ultimate control center for your software projects. This powerful platform gives you unparalleled visibility into every phase of your builds, empowering you to make informed decisions, optimize your processes, and deliver exceptional results."
      },
      {
        "id": "features",
        "order": 5,
        "type": "features",
        "body": "With the Olympus Builder Dashboard, you'll get:\n\n- Real-time tracking of your build status and progress\n- Detailed phase-by-phase timelines to identify bottlenecks\n- Comprehensive agent roster to monitor team productivity\n- Constitutional checks to ensure your builds align with best practices\n- Contextual insights to understand the \"why\" behind your builds"
      },
      {
        "id": "proof",
        "order": 6,
        "type": "proof",
        "components": [
          {
            "type": "testimonial_card",
            "name": "John Doe",
            "title": "CTO, Acme Corp",
            "quote": "The Olympus Builder Dashboard has been a game-changer for our software development team. It's given us unprecedented visibility and control over our builds, allowing us to deliver projects on time and under budget."
          },
          {
            "type": "testimonial_card",
            "name": "Jane Smith",
            "title": "VP of Engineering, Megacorp",
            "quote": "Before Olympus, our builds were a black box. Now, we can quickly identify and address issues before they spiral out of control. It's a must-have tool for any organization serious about software excellence."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "how_it_works",
        "order": 7,
        "type": "how_it_works",
        "body": "Using the Olympus Builder Dashboard is simple:\n\n1. Sign up for your free account\n2. Connect your software projects and watch the magic unfold\n3. Gain unprecedented visibility and control over your builds"
      },
      {
        "id": "guarantee",
        "order": 8,
        "type": "guarantee",
        "body": "We're so confident that the Olympus Builder Dashboard will transform your software development process that we offer a 30-day money-back guarantee. If you're not completely satisfied, simply let us know, and we'll refund your investment, no questions asked."
      },
      {
        "id": "faq",
        "order": 9,
        "type": "faq",
        "body": "Q: What if I don't have the time to set up the Olympus Builder Dashboard?\nA: We understand that your time is precious. That's why we've designed the setup process to be quick and painless. Our onboarding team will guide you through the process step-by-step, ensuring you're up and running in no time.\n\nQ: Does the Olympus Builder Dashboard integrate with my existing tools?\nA: Absolutely! The Olympus Builder Dashboard seamlessly integrates with a wide range of project management, code repositories, and CI/CD tools, allowing you to centralize all your build data in one place."
      },
      {
        "id": "final_cta",
        "order": 10,
        "type": "final_cta",
        "cta": {
          "text": "Get Started Now",
          "style": "primary",
          "urgency": true
        }
      }
    ],
    "above_fold": [
      "hero"
    ],
    "sticky_elements": [
      "cta_bar",
      "countdown"
    ]
  },
